### Load Balancer Cluster (HAProxy)
Enhances redundancy and ensure scalability by distributing load across multiple server 

### Web Server (Nginx)
Handles HTTPS request serves static content and distributes web traffic to improve performance and prevent downtime in the event that a web server  fails

### Application Server 
Executes server sde codes and serve dynamic content for effective load distribution

### Database Server (MySQL Primary - Replica)
Stores and retrieves data from web application by providing data redundancy and high availability
